loved it ! ! okay , first off i make it a point to not say anything about the plot , characters , etc . when writing a review on this site . however , let me say this , i watched the whole series , all 21 episodes , in 2 days ... and yes i have a full time job ! i could not stop watching ! i found that this series , not unlike gantz and a few other that i have recently picked up , was incredible . i would definitely suggest this to anyone who is even remotely into anime . and on a side note , i wounder if one of the animators work on fooly cooly ( sp ? ) . there were several scene where i noticed similaritie